abstract: >-
  Forever — a TypeScript AI agent framework aimed at digital legacy and emotional companions. 16+ LLM adapters, 5 thinking strategies, RAG, MCP, graph workflow, safety guardrails. The 'Forever' name is half-joke, half-ambition.
